# Onchain spelling

- Always write **onchain** (one word, no hyphen).
- Do **not** write **on-chain** in UI copy, comments, docs, metadata, or strings.

## Examples

- ❌ `On-chain tactical fleet combat`
- ✅ `Onchain tactical fleet combat`

- ❌ `on-chain game`
- ✅ `onchain game`

Apply in SEO metadata, Open Graph text, and in-app strings the same way.
